examples.en: Sympathy is not Jack's strong suit.
We were trucking on down to Jack's place.
She's totally insensitive to Jack's feelings.
Jack's got a new car  a red two-seater job.
There was an edge of hostility in Jack's voice.
Jack's private opinion was that she was selfish.
Jack's getting through the ironing at a rate of knots!
I arrived at Jack's suite half an hour ahead of schedule.
Mimi became jealous when Jack's career started taking off.
Jack's having trouble keeping up with the rest of the class.
The family would like to express their thanks to all those who sent messages of sympathy after Jack's tragic accident.
